title: Uber's Traffic Jammed In Netherlands, India And Spain
teaser: Uber says it's reached 52 countries since its 2010 launch, but our number cruncher Mona Chalabi tells NPR's Rachel Martin the tally is changing as some countries try to ban the ride-sharing service.
